				<div class="postbody">
				When you boot from CD with linux; try starting like so:
<br />
</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Code:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="code">linux hda=14593,255,63</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
substitute the 14593 for the actual number of cylinders on your drive,  255 for heads, 63 for sectors.<br />
